Spell Haste 2 is extreemly easy to get, but SH3 or 4 is another story.  For a level 55 shaman with some friends, perhaps the easiest may be a Ring of Dark Intellect from Veksar. You can also buy a SH4 augment with adventure points (Glowing Ore of Rapid Thought).

I suggest looking up Spell Haste on Allahkazam and check out all the items with that effect and see what you can do.

Also, you can look for different focus effects that hasten just certain types of spells. If you want haste for your DoTs alone (Affliction Haste) or buffing alone (Enhancement Haste) or conjuring alone (Conjuring Haste), you can probably find something cheaper for each and it will have a better haste percentage.

Anyway, check out Allahkazam for searching for specific stuff.

